Buyer side

User posts what they want to buy
Other buyers join the buying group
Group reaches a minimum number of buyers
Sellers can offer their best price
Buyers choose the best deal

Seller side

Seller sees active buyer groups
Seller submits price/offer
Best offer gets highlighted
Buyers confirm interest or pay deposit

Core MVP pages

Homepage: “Buy together. Negotiate better.”
Browse active buying groups
Create a buying request
Group detail page
Seller offer dashboard
Login/signup
Admin panel

Recommended student-founder tech stack

Frontend: React / Next.js
Backend: Node.js / Supabase
Database: PostgreSQL
Auth: Supabase Auth / Firebase Auth
Payments later: Razorpay
Hosting: Vercel

First MVP feature set

Create buying group
Join buying group
Show number of interested buyers
Seller quote submission
Basic chat/comment system
Admin approval of requests and sellers

